  <brief_title>Study of the Prednisone Sparing Effect of Xolair (Omalizumab) in Patients With Prednisone-dependent Asthma With Eosinophilic Bronchitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Double Blind Placebo Controlled Trial of the Prednisone Sparing Effect of Xolair (Omalizumab) in Patients With Prednisone-dependent Asthma With Eosinophilic Bronchitis</official_title>
